author: brane
msg: * subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/README: Apache on Windows doesn't
understand crypted passwords. Explain that and give the correct
password entries for Windows.

author: brane
msg: Teach win_tests.py to start *and* stop svnserve if the win32all
Python extension modules are available.
* win_tests.py (start_svnserve): Remove.
(Svnserve): New, replaces start_svnserve. Check for the win32all
modules when starting svnserve, and use those functions to start
and stop the process if they're available.

author: djh
msg: Fix xml blame output to use local path style for non-urls.
* subversion/clients/cmdline/blame-cmd.c
(svn_cl__blame): Convert the output path to local style if needed.

author: lundblad
msg: Fix issue #2153: wc-to-url copies would wrongly include deleted items.
Thanks to Ben Collins-Sussman for various helpful hints.
Original patch by kfogel, tested and modified by me.
* subversion/libsvn_client/commit_util.c
(harvest_committables): If in copy_mode, request deleted entries
too, and set the SVN_CLIENT_COMMIT_ITEM_DELETE flag on them.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/copy_tests.py
(mixed_wc_to_url): New test.
(test_list): Run it.
NOTE: This revision was later reverted in r14753.
